name: I Have A Very Bad Feeling About This
Lore: '''Look at him, he''s heading for that small moon.'' Luke became apprehensive when Obi-Wan informed him, ''That''s no moon. It''s a space station.''',
Text: 'If opponent just deployed four or more characters to same location this turn, prevent all of those characters from battling this turn. OR If opponent just ''reacted'' to a battle, cancel the battle.',
